{"tid":1731514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店唔應該罷工","createTime":"2019-11-17T17:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T23:52:11.000Z","uid":70443,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e3fc8d325b2235f893433f0c6a04ebb28f315599","tid":1731514,"uid":70443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"首先要大大力多謝一眾黃店支持罷工先。<br />\n小弟夢到罷工日子，其實都好需要有地方食飯、休息下嘅。見到其實好多仲開緊嘅都係藍店，可能有手足焗住都要幫襯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以希望各黃店罷工日子就算唔正常營業，都可以開放畀手足。<br />\n<br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救Poly呀DLLM</span></span>"},{"pid":"ad5b794a3c3b7613241502ab8ba3f5133a297eb3","tid":1731514,"uid":280046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:48:42.000Z","msg":"同意 大家要搵錢先支援到啊diu"},{"pid":"bfacb957e64d7f76796a0ddaff3de78a2995b1b9","tid":1731514,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad5b794a3c3b7613241502ab8ba3f5133a297eb3","tid":1731514,"uid":280046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:48:42.000Z","msg":"同意 大家要搵錢先支援到啊diu"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T17:55:28.000Z","msg":"咁講黃絲都唔應該罷工，唔返工點搵到錢支援，推而廣之就係冇人罷工"},{"pid":"d4372593815169ce195470e5bdabd3b90df8c78e","tid":1731514,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T19:29:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1118 全民大三罷 集中post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1731774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1731774</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yY0GhDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyY0GhDa.jpg&h=29cd4986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下大家幫手入去推"},{"pid":"28fb881fd536066d3002afa8fa4ce5edf81f8688","tid":1731514,"uid":70443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T23:52:11.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}